70-8195-11f0-9f7b-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Croatian\n\nHaving grown up by the sea, he developed a deep appreciation for its beauty and the underwater world from an early age, which inspired and shaped his career aspirations. Following elementary school, Marin enrolled in a maritime high school with a clear ambition to pursue a career at sea. After completing the education, he gained valuable hands-on experience working at a gas station for ships, where he strengthened his skills in teamwork, customer service, and communication. Known for being responsible, communicative, and eager to embrace new experiences and challenges, Marin is enthusiastic about continuing to grow and gain further experience in the maritime industry."},{"name":"Matea Galić","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::211b1020-f06c-11ee-81e4-1f741a075b1d::assets::4ae49550-8195-11f0-9f7b-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Croatian\n\nMatea is a professional hostess with two years of experience and a strong passion for delivering outstanding service on yachts. She is highly skilled in providing personalized guest experiences, managing onboard events, and ensuring client satisfaction at the highest level.\n\nA true team player, she works well under pressure and quickly adapts to new situations, consistently maintaining a calm and professional demeanour in dynamic environments."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2430000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2430000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":3360000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3360000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"From 1 January till 23 May, From 3 October till 31 December:","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-05-23T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-10-03T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2430000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lin